          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Elimination of Double Subsidies for the Hardrock Mining Industry Act of 201</b><b>9</b></p> <p> This bill modifies the tax deductions allowed for hardrock mines to prohibit the percentage depletion allowance for hardrock mines located on land currently subject to the general mining laws, or on land patented under such laws.</p>]]></text>
